Subject: Predefined content UK bank account cannot be triggered
Description:
Hello,

We have tried to trigger Bank Account UK predefined content but unsuccessfully.

*8D + 6D with space (12345678 12 34 56)
*8D + 6D and - (12345678 12-34-56)

Can you please let us know what we are doing wrong? In the past, you provided the format for the UK bank account as 8D + 6D with or without spaces).

Thank you!
Csilla
